FRONTEND OF FOOD ORDERING WEBAPP:

* npx create-react-app .
  "." indicates the project will be formed in exsting folder itself rather than creating new one 

* go to Tailwind css website and search for installation cmd
   npm install -D tailwindcss
   npx tailwindcss init  

* paste configuration inside talwind.config.js
  /** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
  module.exports = {
  content: ["./src/**/*.{html,js}"],
  theme: {
    extend: {},
  },
  plugins: [],
  } 
  
* paste tailwind css directives inside index.css
  @tailwind base;
  @tailwind components;
  @tailwind utilities;
  
* To include the Material UI(MUI) 
  npm install @mui/material @emotion/react @emotion/styled
